<p>This is something I had a lot of fun working on. This SCP was a collab with Westrin and Validclay. Both are incredibly amazing to work with, just so you know. This was inspired by cartoons, the dreams and nightmares I had as a child, and the dreams I have nowadays where I'm reading non-existant SCP articles.</p>
<p>This managed to get 64+ in 24 hours without a downvote, which I am honestly really surprised about. I wasn't expecting this silly thing to be enjoyed by so many people in such a short span of time. I am incredibly happy about that.</p>
<p>I fucking love writing villains.</p>
<p>Page Theme: <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2EAXLzKT3zQ">Flash Ram</a> (Thank you for sharing this w/ me faminepulse)</p>
